Nancy Gathungu bụ Auditor General nke mba Kenya, na-amalite ọrụ na onwa June afo 2020. Ọ nọchiri Edward Ouko onye lara ezumike nká n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afo 2019. Ọ rịọrọ ka ọ bụrụ Auditor General n'okpuru iwu afo 2010.

Gathungu bụ onye ọrụ gọọmentị na-arụ ọrụ, sonyeere ọfịs Auditor General na 1993 ma bụrụ onye a na-akwalite n'ọkwa Director Quality Assurance, Ofis nke Auditor General. N'oge nhọpụta, ọ bụ onye na-achọ ịzọ ọkwa PhD na Jomo Kenyatta nke University nke Agriculture n Technology. Degree ndị gara aga gụnyere MBA na Strategic Management na nzere bachelọ nke azụmahịa (Accounting Option).
N'oge ọ malitere ọrụ n'afo 2020, Gathungu nwere ego ruru nde Ksh30.89.
N'onwa 2021, Nancy Gathungu lekọtara akụkọ na-egosi na ọkara nke ijeri KSh 18.5 nke ọnụ ọgụgụ ndị mmadụ nke ụlọ Kenya enweghị ike ịkọwapụta.
